    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/c230b7580f69ef7a03ff3d7b995e3a4f.poster.avif?t=1762245477\" width=800 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/c230b7580f69ef7a03ff3d7b995e3a4f.webm?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/c230b7580f69ef7a03ff3d7b995e3a4f.mp4?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Heart has lost its guiding voice and disappeared alongside it. In its wake, it left a mess of Amalgamation, twisting and corrupting the matter of the Psyche. Guide the Heart's puppet Peccori as through rhythm-infused levels where every action hits to the beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5d288fa85cb48ae48f4099098438d6c2.poster.avif?t=1762245477\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5d288fa85cb48ae48f4099098438d6c2.webm?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5d288fa85cb48ae48f4099098438d6c2.mp4?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your attacks' momentum to sling yourself through enemies and reach new heights! String together air combos, discover new enemy types, and draw ever closer to finding the Heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/a966b34b99fce654257b3e8e8f67c5ee.poster.avif?t=1762245477\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/a966b34b99fce654257b3e8e8f67c5ee.webm?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/a966b34b99fce654257b3e8e8f67c5ee.mp4?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5484418eb2b36113cdaf1b129497f73b.poster.avif?t=1762245477\" width=800 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5484418eb2b36113cdaf1b129497f73b.webm?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/5484418eb2b36113cdaf1b129497f73b.mp4?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Beat, Heart, Beat</i> is a surreal, reflective journey backed by a grungy alt-rock soundtrack. Story Mode is a concept album with cutscenes, characters, and new corners of the mind to explore at every step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/d0a5321f29d8c1d330b74cc4b289d256.poster.avif?t=1762245477\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239360/extras/d0a5321f29d8c1d330b74cc4b289d256.webm?t=1762245477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"ht